casebody.data:
SPECTRUM HEALTH HOSPITALS, Mary Free Bed Rehabilitation Hospital, and Mary Free Bed Medical Group, Plaintiffs-Appellants,
v.
GEICO GENERAL INSURANCE COMPANY and GEICO Indemnity Company, Defendants-Appellees. SC: 158999
COA: 341353 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 10, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the December 11, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
